

Install R language 

		step 1 :- sudo apt-get install r-base


Install Typescript

		step 1 :- npm install typescript


Install Pascal

		step 1 :- sudo apt-get install fpc



Install Mysql

		step 1 :- sudo apt-get install mysql-server



Adding user to mysql

		step 1 :- sudo mysql

		step 2 :- CREATE USER 'sammy'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
			sammy, password is user name and password respectively you can change name as per your requirement

		step 3 :- GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'sammy'@'localhost' WITH GRANT OPTION;
			Granting all permission to the user

		step 4 :- exit




